part_description = "[b]MC PROCESSOR[/b]
Connected missiles may move 1 Zone slower or faster than their listed Speed when Directed. If they move slower, increase the number that needs to be rolled to shoot them down by 1 (normally 3+). If they move faster, decrease the number by 1."
